@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ywtoty(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v0
    v0 = wp.abs(0.19)
    tmp = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.04 + tmp + 0.35) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.85)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.abs(v1 + 0.85)) / 0.52)
    v0 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.19 * v2 + 0.16)) / (wp.cos(v2 + 0.88) * (v0 + 0.27 - tmp + 0.87)))
    data[tid] = v0
